               <p>PATRICK MANNING. I am the son of 
               <persName id="t18320105-200-person1771">
                  John 
                  Manning
               <interp inst="t18320105-200-person1771" type="surname" value="Manning"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18320105-200-person1771" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18320105-200-person1771" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , of Adam and Eve-court, Whitecross-street. On the afternoon of the 4th of January I was by the Flying Horse, in <placeName id="t18320105-200-crimeloc1113">Crown-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18320105-200-crimeloc1113" type="placeName" value="Crown-street"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18320105-200-crimeloc1113" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320105-200-off1111 t18320105-200-crimeloc1113"></join> - I saw the prisoner near Mr. Ray's shop; he took the trousers off the iron rail, and ran away with them - I ran and overtook him, without losing sight of him - a woman picked up the trousers.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18320105-200-person1772">
                  WILLIAM 
                  LOVELACE
               <interp inst="t18320105-200-person1772" type="surname" value="LOVELACE"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18320105-200-person1772" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18320105-200-person1772" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I live in Long-alley. I was coming up Long-alley, and saw the prisoner running - I stopped him; an officer came up, and took him.</p>

               <p>Prisoner. Q. Was no one running before me? A. No.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18320105-200-person1773">
                  THOMAS 
                  HOWARD
               <interp inst="t18320105-200-person1773" type="surname" value="HOWARD"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18320105-200-person1773" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18320105-200-person1773" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
