            . I am foreman to William 
               <persName id="t18320105-200-person1774">
                  David 
                  Ray
               <interp inst="t18320105-200-person1774" type="surname" value="Ray"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18320105-200-person1774" type="given" value="David"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18320105-200-person1774" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             - he is a clothes-saleman. I was standing in the corner of the shop - I saw the rails shake, and the trousers move; I went out, and was told which way the prisoner had gone - I pursued, and saw him running with something - I saw him stopped, and Maxey brought in these trousers; one of the prisoner's companious took the pin out of them.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18320105-200-person1775">
